headline: Triangle Credit Union Prepares for Growth with Jack Henry
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) announced that Triangle Credit Union has chosen Jack Henry's Symitar® platform and complementary products to better serve members and maintain a competitive market position.
